subject: Sys23-2 A talking dog!?
author: Frank Sumption
full_text:
------=_NextPart_000_10a1_4fcb_2bd2
Content-Type: text/plain; format=flowed

Winston is the new Yorkie, and very much alive!! Little bit is like his nick 
name. The chicken is the chicken jerky we've been getting for the dogs. 
Always a surprise.

I think I had the volume up to high with the dual speakers, also later in 
the session I slowed the sweep, I should have left it alittle faster, maybe 
1.5 volts per second change.

Frank
